    dc:creator "Lin, Shan; Yao, Yunzhi; Ren, Dong" ;
    dc:date "2018" ;
    dc:title "A new scale insect of the extinct family Weitschatidae (Insecta: Hemiptera: Coccomorpha) from mid-Cretaceous Burmese amber" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1216664>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1216666> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1216664>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Holotype of Criniverticillus longicumulus Lin, Yao & Ren gen. et sp. nov. CNU-COC-MA2018001. Photomicrographs of (A) dorsal and (B) ventral views; line drawings of (C) dorsal and(D) ventral views.Scale bars = 1.0 mm. afp: anterior flexing patch; dse: dorsal simple eye; en: endophallus; mrt: median ridge on tergite; pfp: posterior flexing patch; sscr: sensorium on subcostal ridge; tp: tubercular projection." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1216664/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1216666>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Detailed photographs of Criniverticillus longicumulus Lin, Yao & Ren gen. et sp. nov. holotype, CNU-COC- MA2018001. (A) dorsal and (B) ventral views of body; (C) left tubercular projection on apex of abdomen in (B); (D) ventral view of right mid- and hind legs; (E) claw, tarsus and part of tibia (note bifurcate setae and spine-likeclaw digitules) in (D); (F) ventral view of antennae; (G) apical antennal segment in (F); (H) lateral view of apex of antenna (note basiconic sensilla); (I) dorsal view offorewing; (J)dorsal view of hamulohalteres.Scale bars for A, B,D, F, I = 0.4 mm; C = 0.05 mm;E, G, H, J = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1216666/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

